data.description: Welcome to your peaceful haven in the heart of Peaceful Acres, Dunnellon! This inviting single-family home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and endless outdoor adventures.    Located in a serene neighborhood with well-maintained paved roads, this property welcomes you with a convenient carport, providing shelter for your truck or car just shy 1/2 acre of land, Plenty of room for a pool.    One of the most prized features of this community is the public boat ramp access, allowing residents to explore the waters of Lake Rousseau, the Withlacoochee River, and the captivating Rainbow River. Anglers will be delighted by the world-class bass fishing opportunities, with the Gulf boat ramp in historic Yankee Town just a short ride away.    Rest assured that this elevated lot is situated in a no-flood zone, offering both peace of mind and security for your investment.    For outdoor enthusiasts, the possibilities are boundless. Within a convenient 2-hour radius, you can immerse yourself in the natural beauty of eight unique springs, ideal for kayaking and boating adventures. The nearby Goethe State Forest provides endless opportunities for exploration and connection with nature.    For everyday convenience, you're only a 9-minute drive from the breathtaking Rainbow River and less than 10 minutes from the heart of downtown Dunnellon, where you can discover local shops, savor delectable dining, and enjoy entertainment options.    Privacy is a cherished aspect of this property, as it opens to a picturesque field often used for pastures, offering a peaceful and open view with no backyard neighbors.    This well-maintained home boasts numerous thoughtful updates. The roof was redone in 2015,a kitchen remodel in 2016, and a master suite renovation in 2016.The air handler and compressor were replaced in 2016, a hot water tank replaced in 2016, New floors 2016. And additional improvements include a water softener added in 2020 The new septic field, installed in 2021 and cleaned in the same year, ensures efficiency and peace of mind. and recent enhancements include a new well pump in 2023, a freshly sealed driveway, newly painted exterior, new shutters 2023.    In summary, this single-family home in Peaceful Acres offers the perfect combination of comfort and adventure. With its exceptional location, meticulous updates, and serene surroundings, it's a haven for those seeking the quintessential Dunnellon lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make it your own and start living your Florida dream today!
